title: N. Korea confirms test of missile capable of striking Guam - Associated Press
content: N. Korea confirms test of missile capable of striking Guam  Associated PressView Full Coverage on Google News
description: SEOUL, South Korea (AP) — North Korea confirmed Monday it test-launched an intermediate-range ballistic missile capable of reaching the U.S. territory of Guam, the North’s most significant weapon launch in years, as Washington plans steps to show its commitment to its Asian allies.
